div2.entryFree:

      قَبْلُ Before; contr. of بَعْدُ; (S, K, &c.;) an
adv. n. of time; and, as some say, of place also;
(MF, TA;) and of rank, or station. (TA.)

sense.dictScrap:
 A body of men from one father and
mother: and ↓ قَبِيلٌ, without ة, a body of men
from several ancestors. (Az in TA, art. سبط.)

 He was, or became, or went, before,
or ahead; preceded; had, or took, precedence;
contr. of تَأَخَّرَ, q. v. See 1.

div2.entryFree:

      قَيْصُومٌ Artemisia abrotanum, or southern-wood;
also called قَيْصُومٌ ذَكَرٌ: and قَيْصُومٌ أُنْثَى is
applied to santolina.

sense.dictScrap:
 --
       --  [Thus it signifies He decreed  a thing;
ordained it; pronounced it; or decided it judicially.]

 --
       --  [He completed; accomplished;
or fully performed; a thing.]

 --
       --  You also say, حَكَمَ بِهِ He decreed it; &c.;
like حَكَمَ بِهِ: see an ex. voce سُلْطَانٌ.

 --
       --  إِقْتَضَيْتُ مِنْهُ حَقِّى I took, or received,
from him my due. (Mgh, Msb.)

 --
       --  اِسْتَقَلَّ He was independent of all others;
absolute.

 --
       --  I. q. بَاذِ نْجَانٌ;
(IAar, K:) as also كَهْكَبٌ. (TA.)

 --
       --  قَامَ وَقَعَدَ: see قَعَدَ; and أَقْعَدَهُ;
and see an ex. voce سُدَّةٌ.

div2.entryFree:

      كَرِيهٌ Disliked, disapproved of, blamed, or
hated; hateful, blameable, displeasing, or odious;
as also ↓ مَكْرُوهٌ.


      كَعْكٌ A well-known bread; (K;) biscuit;
(MA;) or [a kind of] dry bread: (MA, TA:)
now applied to a sort of bread made in the form
of a ring, hollow, [and generally containing some
دبس or the like,] the best of which is brought
from Syria, and given as a present. (TA.)


      كِفَافَةٌ [app. a subst., not an inf. n.,] The act,
or art, of sewing in the manner termed كَفٌّ;
(TA;) contr. of شِلَاشَةٌ. (TA in art. شل.)

sense.dictScrap:
 Relating to all or the whole; universal;
total: and often meaning relating to the generality;
general; contr. of جُزْئِىٌّ.

 --
       --  لِسَانٌ كَلِيلٌ A dull tongue;
lacking sharpness. (S. *)

 --
       --  A task;
compulsory work; a duty imposed.

div2.entryFree:

      مِكْيَالٌ A measure with which corn is measured;
(S, Msb, K;) as also ↓ كَيْلٌ; (Msb;) a measure
of capacity.
